1
00:00:12,760 --> 00:00:14,360
What could leave deep marks?

2
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:22,960
A pulley system.

3
00:00:23,728 --> 00:00:25,000
The killer rigged a pulley

4
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,160
to the tree

5
00:00:26,520 --> 00:00:28,000
and used a long hemp rope

6
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,280
to tie one end

7
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,480
around Lu Ruiheng's neck.

8
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,560
=Cases Between Us=

9
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:37,720
The other end was attached to a vehicle.

10
00:00:37,720 --> 00:00:38,900
=Episode 11=

11
00:01:02,360 --> 00:01:02,880
Zhao Cai.

12
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,080
Tell them

13
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:05,120
what you found.

14
00:01:05,130 --> 00:01:07,350
The Young Master had me ask around
all over Baishu Street.

15
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,200
An old handyman at this shop said...

16
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:14,000
Around 1 AM,

17
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:16,800
I heard a car outside.

18
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:19,000
The engine suddenly roared
and woke me up.

19
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,880
I'm not a light sleeper,

20
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,600
but it was too loud.

21
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,240
Anything else?

22
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:26,800
Anything else?

23
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:28,640
I don't think so.

24
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,520
Cars pass by at night.

25
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,720
That's normal, isn't it?

26
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:35,800
They all said it was the engine.

27
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:36,240
Right.

28
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:37,520
Three people heard it.

29
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:38,840
It was in the middle of the night.

30
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,320
And they heard it twice.

31
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:41,480
About ten minutes apart.

32
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,160
The first time,

33
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:47,000
the killer used a vehicle
to hoist the body.

34
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,360
The second time, he drove away.

35
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,280
What kind of engine was loud enough

36
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,880
to wake people indoors?

37
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:53,760
That's the key.

38
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,480
The killer definitely wasn't driving

39
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,560
a well-built Ford sedan.

40
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,800
It had to be a noisy,

41
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,520
high-powered truck.

42
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:10,720
Things like pulleys

43
00:02:10,920 --> 00:02:12,240
and hemp ropes

44
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,824
are commonly used for hauling cargo too.

45
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,640
That narrows down
the killer's profession.

46
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,800
But something still doesn't add up.

47
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,200
Lu Ruiheng

48
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,920
never resisted.

49
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:23,120
He was unconscious?

50
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:32,720
You said he'd been drinking
before he died.

51
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:33,640
Right.

52
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:36,160
But not enough to get him drunk.

53
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,840
Madam Feng said

54
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,640
he'd had a bottle of aphrodisiac liquor.

55
00:02:39,650 --> 00:02:41,600
Could it have something to do
with the ingredients?

56
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,400
Can you test it?

57
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,680
I can try.

58
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,280
But once alcohol enters the body,

59
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,240
it's absorbed.

60
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:49,800
Whether there's enough left
to identify is pure luck.

61
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,200
Let's check the tonic shop.

62
00:03:11,568 --> 00:03:13,232
(Temporarily out. Back soon.)
Let's wait.

63
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:16,780
(Tiger Bone Five-Poison
Restore Your Manhood.)

64
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,160
Reminded you of something?

65
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,200
Extra!

66
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:31,600
Rich playboy found hanged!

67
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:34,080
Notorious brothel patron
hanged from ancient tree!

68
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,480
One paper, please.

69
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:42,360
(Ping Daily)
The Vengeful Ghost of the Eight Alleys.

70
00:03:42,656 --> 00:03:45,120
Lu Ruiheng was a wealthy playboy
who frequented brothels.

71
00:03:45,136 --> 00:03:47,232
He raped Qiao'er,
driving her to hang herself.

72
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,680
Huang Erya was a human trafficker.

73
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,840
She and her son, Huang Cheng,
worked together,

74
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:53,280
luring young women

75
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,720
with promises of work,

76
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,320
and then selling them
to the Eight Alleys

77
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,240
for profit.

78
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,680
The murder only happened today.

79
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,680
Newspapers close around three or four.

80
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,880
How could the reporter

81
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:03,760
have learned all this

82
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:05,040
in just a few hours?

83
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,080
Either the reporter is the killer

84
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,360
or knows the killer.

85
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,840
(Reported by Han Zhenzhu)
Han Zhenzhu...

86
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:19,400
You know this person?

87
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,760
No.

88
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,200
You don't?

89
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,360
I... I really don't.

90
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,720
Buying liquor?

91
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:38,880
Come on in.

92
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,560
Come in.

93
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:45,580
(Nong's Medicinal Liquor Shop)

94
00:04:47,300 --> 00:04:49,500
(Tiger Bone Five-Poison
Restore Your Manhood.)

95
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:20,160
How have you been?

96
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,000
Pretty good.

97
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:24,960
Need anything?

98
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:26,520
No.

99
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:27,960
You do?

100
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,160
I don't.

101
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:38,320
If I remember right, you have a friend

102
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,400
named Han Zhenzhu.

103
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,000
Wasn't she in Hubei?

104
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,080
When did she come to Beijing?

105
00:05:45,100 --> 00:05:47,700
Her father kept pressuring her to marry.
She came here to hide out.

106
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,480
What's she up to lately?

107
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,440
You're not her type.

108
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,040
What type am I?

109
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,120
A pretty boy

110
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,880
who can't lift a thing.

111
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,640
Now tell me.

112
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,840
Why are you looking for her?

113
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,920
It's related to a case.

114
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:18,760
Confidential.

115
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,720
Fine, I'll tell you.

116
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,400
Take a look at this.

117
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:26,048
(The Vengeful Ghost of the Eight Alleys)

118
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,860
(Reported by Han Zhenzhu)

119
00:06:30,896 --> 00:06:32,192
You gave her the exclusive?

120
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,360
If I'd given her the exclusive,

121
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,704
why would I be asking you about her?

122
00:06:34,736 --> 00:06:35,760
Was it Yuan Hong?

123
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:38,520
I had no idea.

124
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,320
Hello?

125
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,440
Han Zhenzhu is with me.

126
00:06:44,180 --> 00:06:46,580
(Jingshi Police Department)

127
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:04,320
(Han Zhenzhu)

128
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:06,160
Well, isn't this Missy Zhao?

129
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,160
You've gotten taller.

130
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:13,400
You know each other?

131
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:15,000
- Not really.
- We go way back.

132
00:07:22,144 --> 00:07:23,560
She's an old friend of my sister's.

133
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,960
It's been years.

134
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,560
What a surprise.

135
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,680
You haven't changed a bit.

136
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:33,080
Now that you're older,

137
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:35,080
you finally know how good I am?

138
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,280
I've known that since I was a kid.

139
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,560
Anyway,

140
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:44,120
we wanted to ask you about something.

141
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,720
Your article described

142
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,160
the rules of the Eight Alleys so well.

143
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,512
(The Vengeful Ghost of the Eight Alleys)
Mind telling us

144
00:07:48,520 --> 00:07:49,696
where you got your information?

145
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,200
Firsthand experience.

146
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,600
I've spent the past few months

147
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:02,600
visiting brothels disguised as a man.

148
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:06,640
I wanted to write a documentary series

149
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,240
about the Eight Alleys

150
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:10,200
and the women there.

151
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,520
For months,

152
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:13,040
I got nowhere.

153
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:16,440
Until yesterday,

154
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,120
when I met a girl

155
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:21,360
on Baishu Street.

156
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:22,800
Mister,

157
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,680
did you hear anything last night?

158
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,680
I heard

159
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,240
a car,

160
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,160
and then I went back to sleep.

161
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,600
Excuse me.

162
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,760
Are you Reporter Han?

163
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:41,000
She was kidnapped
by Huang Erya and Huang Cheng

164
00:08:41,008 --> 00:08:42,880
and sold to the Handan Pleasure House.

165
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,520
Luckily, her family found her

166
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:46,560
and bought her freedom.

167
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,960
She's the one who told me

168
00:08:51,248 --> 00:08:52,600
about what happened to Qiao'er.

169
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:03,560
Do you know

170
00:09:04,112 --> 00:09:05,800
where the trafficking network starts?

171
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,120
The Eight Alleys.

172
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,080
Exactly.

173
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,000
There's enormous profit

174
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,840
in this business.

175
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:20,280
The brothel owners all work together,

176
00:09:20,280 --> 00:09:21,760
forming an underground network.

177
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,600
For local girls, getting out alive

178
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,600
is already lucky.

179
00:09:24,704 --> 00:09:25,920
For girls from out of town,

180
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,520
or those sold by their own families,

181
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,960
there's almost no hope.

182
00:09:30,710 --> 00:09:32,180
What if we raid them without warning?

183
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:32,800
Do you think...

184
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:33,560
It won't work.

185
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:35,000
They've prepared

186
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,520
for every scenario.

187
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,760
Even if you arrest them,

188
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,440
the victims won't testify in court.

189
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,400
Their legal defenses

190
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,760
are airtight.

191
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,320
Even if you take them to court,

192
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,360
you might still lose.

193
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:49,680
Besides,

194
00:09:49,808 --> 00:09:51,536
they might even turn it against you.

195
00:09:51,616 --> 00:09:54,080
That's exactly how the former chief
of Division Three went down.

196
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,000
Do you know

197
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,320
what "Handan" means?

198
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:06,670
Lotus.

199
00:10:06,670 --> 00:10:08,560
A lotus that's just about to bloom.

200
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,800
After what happened to Qiao'er,

201
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,320
which scared Lu Ruiheng out of his wits,

202
00:10:12,336 --> 00:10:14,430
why did he still want to go to
Handan Pleasure House?

203
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,040
Because the girls there

204
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:22,080
were all very young.

205
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:25,400
That sick scoundrel likes them that way.

206
00:10:28,736 --> 00:10:30,720
Would it be possible for us
to meet that girl?

207
00:10:32,352 --> 00:10:33,760
She doesn't want to be disturbed.

208
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,840
Soon,

209
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,880
I'll be publishing

210
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:40,120
more of her story.

211
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,160
It's time these ugly truths

212
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,640
came to light.

213
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:15,280
(Jingshi Police Department)

214
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:16,760
My sister said

215
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,480
you know Xia Jinshu,
the hair salon owner.

216
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,080
I once tried to interview her,

217
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,440
but she turned me down.

218
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,360
Your sister tried, too.

219
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,360
She got rejected as well.

220
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,792
She doesn't want to revisit her past?

221
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,000
How do you know?

222
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,400
Your sister told you?

223
00:11:31,856 --> 00:11:32,848
Having worked in a brothel

224
00:11:32,912 --> 00:11:34,520
isn't something she's proud of,
after all.

225
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:36,240
Even remembering it
must be painful enough.

226
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,560
While researching, I found

227
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:43,280
that many girls weren't trapped there.

228
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,360
They chose to stay.

229
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:49,440
Forced to entertain men
since their early teens,

230
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:51,120
they had no skills

231
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:52,920
and no sense of independence.

232
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,160
Leaving the only life they knew,

233
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:56,760
they had no way to survive.

234
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:01,480
Which brothel was Xia Jinshu in?

235
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,520
Handan Pleasure House.

236
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,040
She got out three years ago.

237
00:12:04,208 --> 00:12:05,360
She spent a year in Xianghe

238
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,600
learning hairdressing

239
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,600
before opening her salon.

240
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,400
That doesn't seem

241
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:11,240
connected to Qiao'er.

242
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,320
Consultant Zhao.

243
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,840
Chief said

244
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,240
he contacted Lu Ruiheng's wife.

245
00:12:20,624 --> 00:12:22,110
(International Hotel)
Why is she staying at a hotel

246
00:12:22,128 --> 00:12:23,424
instead of going home?

247
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,000
Honestly,

248
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,360
I'm pretty happy.

249
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:29,760
Really.

250
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,000
Why is there music playing?

251
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,920
Her husband's dead,
and she's celebrating?

252
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:38,920
Maybe that's good news to her.

253
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,840
I'd say so.

254
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:43,340
(Ling Qiu, Wife of Lu Ruiheng)

255
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,680
Madam, someone's here to see you.

256
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,480
I'll talk to you another time.

257
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:47,560
We'll meet again.

258
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:51,840
Hello.

259
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:54,368
You two are?

260
00:12:54,370 --> 00:12:55,390
I'm Chief of Division Four,

261
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,960
- Jingshi Police Department.
- Yuan Hong.

262
00:13:10,162 --> 00:13:10,922
Xie Qing?

263
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,440
What are you doing here?

264
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,280
(Xie Qing)

265
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,480
You scared me.

266
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,520
You know each other?

267
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,680
We studied abroad together.

268
00:13:17,680 --> 00:13:19,640
The only Chinese female officer
in Woolwich.

269
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,080
It's been years.

270
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:24,120
Need backup

271
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,200
to spar with me now?

272
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,720
And this is?

273
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,120
Zhao Shaoshang.

274
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:32,384
Special Investigative Consultant.

275
00:13:38,880 --> 00:13:39,800
So you do remember me.

276
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:45,360
Anyone else would've thought
I was invisible.

277
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,944
I'm the Special
Investigative Consultant.

278
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:53,280
Nice to meet you.

279
00:13:58,570 --> 00:13:59,720
That's a pretty weak handshake.

280
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,840
Are you really a cop?

281
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,760
I use my brain,

282
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:07,960
not brawn.

283
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:18,440
What a small world.

284
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,560
Please, have a seat.

285
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:20,440
Two coffees, please.

286
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:20,960
Yes.

287
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,920
Please.

288
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,360
What brings you here today?

289
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,200
I thought your family ran a factory.

290
00:14:32,880 --> 00:14:33,440
That's right.

291
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,840
Young Lady Xie's family owns
a cosmetics company.

292
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:36,800
I've got

293
00:14:36,944 --> 00:14:38,112
some money to invest now,

294
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:40,080
so I'm thinking about
opening a factory in Beijing.

295
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:42,080
I had someone set up a meeting with her.

296
00:14:42,190 --> 00:14:43,600
(Xie's Cosmetic Factory)
I was hoping

297
00:14:43,610 --> 00:14:45,856
(Mulian Hair Oil)
we could have a chance to work together.

298
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,280
This hair oil is excellent.

299
00:14:53,680 --> 00:14:55,760
It's just hard to find in Beijing.

300
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,480
It's our newest product.

301
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:58,360
That's right.

302
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,120
I bought a tin

303
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:01,120
at a ladies' hair salon before.

304
00:15:01,184 --> 00:15:02,360
The one I told you about.

305
00:15:02,896 --> 00:15:04,120
That was my younger sister.

306
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:06,120
She came to Beijing to have some fun,

307
00:15:06,130 --> 00:15:07,640
(Shengxiamei Hair Salon)
got a haircut,

308
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:09,040
chatted with a few people,

309
00:15:09,248 --> 00:15:11,488
(Mulian Hair Oil)
and promoted our family business.

310
00:15:11,860 --> 00:15:13,380
(Mulian Hair Oil)

311
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:15,240
Shengxiamei Hair Salon?

312
00:15:20,096 --> 00:15:22,360
Young Master Zhao, you keep up
with the times, huh?

313
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:38,720
(International Hotel)

314
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,920
Ling Qiu's alibi checks out.

315
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,480
We can rule her out.

316
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:44,000
If she'd wanted Lu Ruiheng dead,

317
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,360
he would've been dead long ago.

318
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:47,880
Still, it wasn't a total loss.

319
00:15:48,224 --> 00:15:50,320
Go to the Handan Pleasure House
and bring Man here.

320
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:52,240
They might not let her go.

321
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:53,456
They wouldn't before

322
00:15:53,472 --> 00:15:54,528
because they were afraid Man

323
00:15:54,544 --> 00:15:56,200
would expose their ties
to the traffickers.

324
00:15:56,256 --> 00:15:57,700
Now that people keep turning up dead,

325
00:15:57,728 --> 00:15:59,960
if they still refuse to cooperate,
who knows who's next?

326
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:04,580
(International Hotel)

327
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:05,920
Xie Qing.

328
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:07,680
Hope in.

329
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:08,520
We'll give you a ride.

330
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:14,800
Do you mind?

331
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:16,480
Not at all.

332
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:47,680
No ice.

333
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:48,768
You'll have to make do.

334
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:57,760
I'm thirsty, too.

335
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,120
No more.

336
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:03,296
You'll have to tough it out.

337
00:17:12,040 --> 00:17:13,520
So you're staying in Beijing now?

338
00:17:15,840 --> 00:17:16,680
I'm mainly here

339
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,360
because of my sister.

340
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:20,080
What happened to her?

341
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:21,680
She wants to be a singer.

342
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:24,240
My father wanted her

343
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:25,640
to help me promote our products,

344
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,720
but she wasn't interested.

345
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:27,960
We argued,

346
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,560
and she ran away to Beijing.

347
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:31,360
If she wants to sing,

348
00:17:32,608 --> 00:17:34,320
wouldn't Shanghai be a better choice?

349
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:37,240
She didn't take much money with her.

350
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:38,760
She hitched a ride to Beijing.

351
00:17:38,760 --> 00:17:40,120
Later, she called home

352
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:42,000
and said she'd get a job here,

353
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,680
save some money,
and then head to Shanghai.

354
00:17:44,864 --> 00:17:45,920
Do you have a photo of her?

355
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:46,672
I can help you look.

356
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,120
No need.

357
00:17:48,120 --> 00:17:49,040
I've already found her.

358
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,720
That's good.

359
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,800
Chief Yuan has a warm heart.

360
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,440
He's always happy to help.

361
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:17,800
My sister's shy.

362
00:18:17,800 --> 00:18:20,256
She doesn't like meeting strangers,
so I won't invite you in.

363
00:18:20,592 --> 00:18:21,920
I had someone bring back

364
00:18:21,984 --> 00:18:23,880
your favorite Scotch whisky
from Britain.

365
00:18:23,936 --> 00:18:25,344
Let's get together another day.

366
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:26,880
See you.

367
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:49,520
Scoot over.

368
00:18:56,128 --> 00:18:57,680
Not like I want to sit next to you.

369
00:19:13,380 --> 00:19:16,260
(End of Episode 11)

370
00:19:16,601 --> 00:19:18,241
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

371
00:19:18,241 --> 00:19:19,781
♪Troubled times
are but a laughing matter♪

372
00:19:19,781 --> 00:19:21,031
♪However, the world changes♪

373
00:19:21,031 --> 00:19:22,951
♪You'll still be by my side♪

374
00:19:22,951 --> 00:19:24,641
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

375
00:19:24,641 --> 00:19:26,211
♪Praise and blame come and go♪

376
00:19:26,211 --> 00:19:27,781
♪If this is my final chapter♪

377
00:19:27,781 --> 00:19:30,281
♪I'll solve this mystery with you♪
